    return to reference <#src-publicity-privacy-or-moral-rights>
    *publicity, privacy, or moral rights * — You may need to get
    additional permissions before using the material as you intend.
      o More info <https://wiki.creativecommons.org/
        Considerations_for_licensors_and_licensees>

